Symbol.Script_3D:
! Propeller Fan
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = -1 THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 ! Detailed IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Откл.` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 ENDIF
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 THEN END
res = 24 ! Detailed IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 THEN res = 8 ! Simple
IF useSysMat THEN MainBoxMaterial = sMat MATERIAL MainBoxMaterial PEN gs_cont_pen RESOL res
addStatus = 0 IF GLOB_CONTEXT > 40 AND GLOB_CONTEXT < 50 THEN addStatus = 3 ENDIF
! --- HOTSPOT --- !
unID = 1 HOTSPOT 0, -dTDepth/2-propellerDepth, dTHeight/2-propellerDia/2, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -propellerDia/2, -dTDepth/2-propellerDepth, dTHeight/2, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT propellerDia/2, -dTDepth/2-propellerDepth, dTHeight/2, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0, -dTDepth/2-propellerDepth, dTHeight/2+propellerDia/2, unID: unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT -dTWidth/2, -dTDepth/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -dTWidth/2, -dTDepth/2, dTHeight, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT dTWidth/2, -dTDepth/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT dTWidth/2, -dTDepth/2, dTHeight, unID: unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT -dTWidth/2, dTDepth/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -dTWidth/2, dTDepth/2, dTHeight, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT dTWidth/2, dTDepth/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT dTWidth/2, dTDepth/2, dTHeight, unID: unID=unID+1
! --- MAIN BOX --- !
ADDz dTHeight/2 IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 THEN ROTx 90 ADDz -dTDepth/2
EXTRUDE 5, 0, 0, dTDepth, addStatus+16+32, -dTWidth/2, -dTHeight/2, 0, dTWidth/2, -dTHeight/2, 0, dTWidth/2, dTHeight/2, 0, -dTWidth/2, dTHeight/2, 0, -dTWidth/2, -dTHeight/2, -1
ADDz dTDepth
POLY_ 7, -dTWidth/2, -dTHeight/2, 0, dTWidth/2, -dTHeight/2, 0, dTWidth/2, dTHeight/2, 0, -dTWidth/2, dTHeight/2, 0, -dTWidth/2, -dTHeight/2, -1, 0, 0, 900, propellerDia/2, 360, 4000
EXTRUDE 2, 0, 0, propellerDepth, addStatus+16+32, 0, 0, 901, propellerDia/2, 360, 4001
RESOL res/2 CYLIND propellerDepth, propellerCDia/2
FOR i = 1 TO 4 ROTz 45+90*(i-1) ADD propellerCDia/3, 0, propellerDepth*0.95 ROTy 90+ATN((propellerCDia*2/3)/(propellerDepth*0.75)) RECT SQR((propellerDepth*0.75)^2+(propellerCDia*2/3)^2), (propellerDia/2)-0.015*(dTWidth/0.625) DEL 3 NEXT i
ADDz -axisLength RESOL res/3 CYLIND axisLength, axisDia/2 ADDz -cwheelThick RESOL res CYLIND cwheelThick, cwheelDia/2 DEL 2
ADD -dTWidth/2+engineDist, -dTHeight/2+engineDist, -axisLength+ewheelThick CYLIND engineLength, engineDia/2 ADDz -ewheelThick RESOL res/3 CYLIND ewheelThick, axisDia/2 ADDz -ewheelThick RESOL res CYLIND ewheelThick, ewheelDia/2 DEL 3
ADDz -cwheelThick*0.9-axisLength MUL dTWidth/0.625, dTWidth/0.625, 1 EXTRUDE 5, 0, 0, cwheelThick*0.8, 16+32, 0.0465663864264, -0.06261365774744, 1, -0.1583310271203, -0.2149978576208, 1, -0.2149978576208, -0.1583310271203, 1001, -0.06261365774744, 0.0465663864264, 1, 0.0465663864264, -0.06261365774744, 1001 DEL 2
ADD -dTWidth/2+0.12*(dTWidth/0.625), dTHeight/2-0.04*(dTWidth/0.625), 0 MUL dTWidth/0.625, dTWidth/0.625, dTWidth/0.625 ROTz -ATN((dTHeight-0.145)/(dTWidth-0.17)) ROTx -90 POLY_ 8, 0, 0.0001, 1, 0, 0.08+0.075, 1, 0.66, 0.08+0.075, 1, 0.66, 0.0001, 1, 0.61, 0.0001, 1, 0.61, 0.03+0.075, 1, 0.05, 0.03+0.075, 1, 0.05, 0.0001, 1 ADDx 0.396 ROTy 90-(6*((0.50-dTWidth)/0.25))*(dTWidth < 0.50) POLY_ 7, 0.001, 0.08+0.075, 1, 0.001, 0.03+0.075, 1, 0.325, 0.03+0.075, 1, 0.325, 0.0001, 1, 0.375, 0.0001, 1, 0.375, 0.205+0.075, 1, 0.125, 0.205+0.075, 1 DEL 6
DEL 3 ELSE ADD -dTWidth*0.45, dTDepth/2, -dTHeight*0.45 BLOCK dTWidth*0.9, cwheelThick+axisLength-dTDepth, dTHeight*0.9 DEL 1 ADD -dTWidth/2, -dTDepth/2, -dTHeight/2 BLOCK dTWidth, dTDepth, dTHeight DEL 1 ADD -propellerDia/2, -dTDepth/2-propellerDepth, -propellerDia/2 BLOCK propellerDia, propellerDepth, propellerDia DEL 1 ENDIF DEL 1
! --- CONNECTIONS --- !
CALL "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram, ui_current_con = ui_current_con, MEP_NumberConnections = MEP_NumberConnections, MEP_NumConnectionData = gs_Connections, gs_AddConnections = gs_AddConnections, cShow3D = 1, gs_ConMat = MainBoxMaterial, MEP_InsShow = 0, MEP_cline_show_3D = 0, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, ConPosX_1=ConPosX_1, ConPosY_1=ConPosY_1, ConPosZ_1=ConPosZ_1, ConLength_1=ConLength_1, ConEdit_1 = 0, ConPosX_2=ConPosX_2, ConPosY_2=ConPosY_2, ConPosZ_2=ConPosZ_2, ConLength_2=ConLength_2, ConEdit_2 = 0 END
Symbol.Script_2D:
! Propeller Fan
PEN gs_cont_pen SET FILL gs_fill_type
unID = 1 HOTSPOT2 0, 0, unID: unID=unID+1
DrawingNum = 1 IF DrawingNum = 1 THEN ! Top
! --- HOTSPOTS --- !
HOTSPOT2 -dTWidth*0.45, cwheelThick+axisLength-dTDepth/2, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 dTWidth*0.45, cwheelThick+axisLength-dTDepth/2, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 -dTWidth/2, -dTDepth/2, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 -dTWidth/2, dTDepth/2, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 dTWidth/2, dTDepth/2, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 dTWidth/2, -dTDepth/2, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 -propellerDia/2, -dTDepth/2-propellerDepth, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 propellerDia/2, -dTDepth/2-propellerDepth, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 -propellerDia/2, -dTDepth/2-propellerDepth, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 propellerDia/2, -dTDepth/2-propellerDepth, unID: unID=unID+1
! --- MAIN BOX --- !
PUT -dTWidth*0.45, dTDepth/2, 1, -dTWidth*0.45, -dTDepth/2+cwheelThick+axisLength, 1, dTWidth*0.45, -dTDepth/2+cwheelThick+axisLength, 1, dTWidth*0.45, dTDepth/2, 1, -dTWidth*0.45, dTDepth/2, -1
POLY2_B NSP/3, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen,
GET (NSP)
PUT -dTWidth/2, -dTDepth/2, 1, -dTWidth/2, dTDepth/2, 1, dTWidth/2, dTDepth/2, 1, dTWidth/2, -dTDepth/2, 1, -dTWidth/2, -dTDepth/2, -1
POLY2_B NSP/3, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen,
GET (NSP)
PUT -propellerDia/2, -dTDepth/2, 1, -propellerDia/2, -dTDepth/2-propellerDepth, 1, propellerDia/2, -dTDepth/2-propellerDepth, 1, propellerDia/2, -dTDepth/2, 1, -propellerDia/2, -dTDepth/2, -1
POLY2_B NSP/3, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen,
GET (NSP) ENDIF
! --- OTHER VIEWS --- !
ROT2 -SYMB_ROTANGLE * (DrawingNum > 1 AND NOT(SYMB_MIRRORED))+SYMB_ROTANGLE * (DrawingNum > 1 AND SYMB_MIRRORED)
IF DrawingNum = 2 THEN PROJECT2 -3, 90, 2 ! Bottom IF DrawingNum = 3 THEN PROJECT2 4, 270, 2 ! Front IF DrawingNum = 4 THEN PROJECT2 4, 90, 2 ! Back IF DrawingNum = 5 THEN PROJECT2 4, 180*(SYMB_MIRRORED), 2 ! Right IF DrawingNum = 6 THEN PROJECT2 4, 180*NOT(SYMB_MIRRORED), 2 ! Left
! --- CONNECTIONS --- !
CALL "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram, ui_current_con = ui_current_con, MEP_NumberConnections = MEP_NumberConnections, MEP_NumConnectionData = gs_Connections, gs_AddConnections = gs_AddConnections, DrawingNum = DrawingNum, MEP_InsShow = 0, MEP_cline_show = 0, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, gs_fill_type=gs_fill_type, gs_fill_pen=gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen=gs_back_pen, ConPosX_1=ConPosX_1, ConPosY_1=ConPosY_1, ConLength_1=ConLength_1, ConEdit_1 = 0, ConPosX_2=ConPosX_2, ConPosY_2=ConPosY_2, ConLength_2=ConLength_2, ConEdit_2 = 0 DEL 1
END
